Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:47.67,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}いっそぎゅっと　抱きしめて彼方まで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:01:51.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}-You must be here now-
