Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:25.29,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Calling you Calling you Everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:28.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}謳え　叫べ　彷徨い人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:31.96,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}遥かな願いへと
